♪ I roamed and rambled ♪

01:30:06.109 --> 01:30:09.361
♪ I followed my footsteps ♪

01:30:09.404 --> 01:30:12.864
♪ Through
the sparkling sands of ♪

01:30:12.907 --> 01:30:16.118
♪ Her diamond deserts ♪

